Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types_A_WMCC" parameters all
values "B" range (0,)
values "ApplType" stApplType values "ApplType_m" APPLTYPE_MICROWAVE_OVEN, APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN, APPLTYPE_COMB_MICOVEN, APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ApplType" then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_MICROWAVE_OVEN if ApplType = stApplType[2] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN if ApplType = stApplType[3] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_COMB_MICOVEN if ApplType = stApplType[4] then ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN parameters ApplType_m = ApplType_m else ApplType_m = max(min(ApplType_m,4),1) parameters ApplType = stApplType[ApplType_m] endif
values "OvenDoorStyle" stOvenDoorStyle values "ApplStyle_m" OVENDOOR_STYLE_1, OVENDOOR_STYLE_2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "OvenDoorStyle" then ApplStyle_m = OVENDOOR_STYLE_1 if OvenDoorStyle = stOvenDoorStyle[2] then ApplStyle_m = OVENDOOR_STYLE_2 parameters ApplStyle_m = ApplStyle_m else if ApplStyle_m = OVENDOOR_STYLE_1 then OvenDoorStyle = stOvenDoorStyle[1] else OvenDoorStyle = stOvenDoorStyle[2] endif parameters OvenDoorStyle = OvenDoorStyle endif
values "gs_detlevel_3D" stDetlevel3D ! Off(0), Simple(1), Detailed(2) values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DET3D_OFF, DET3D_SIMPLE, DET3D_DETAILED
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_OFF if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetlevel3D[2] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_SIMPLE if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetlevel3D[1] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = DET3D_DETAILED parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D_m = max(min(gs_detlevel_3D_m,2),0) parameters gs_detlevel_3D = stDetlevel3D[3-gs_detlevel_3D_m] endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ApplType" | GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ApplType_m" then
if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_MICROWAVE_OVEN then ZZYZX=0.4 PARAMETERS A=0.6 , ZZYZX=0.4 A=0.6 ENDIF
if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_SINGLE_OVEN then ZZYZX=0.4 PARAMETERS ApplHeight=0.5, ZZYZX=0.4 ApplHeight=0.5 ENDIF
if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_COMB_MICOVEN then PARAMETERS A=0.6 , ZZYZX=0.8 A=0.6 ZZYZX=0.8 ENDIF
if ApplType_m = APPLTYPE_DOUBLE_OVEN then PARAMETERS A=0.6 , ZZYZX=0.9 A=0.6 ZZYZX=0.9 ENDIF
ENDIF
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
if ApplStyle_m = OVENDOOR_STYLE_1 then HIDEPARAMETER "SwitchMat" LOCK "SwitchMat" ENDIF
IF not(Appl2D) THEN hideparameter "ApplLineType", "ApplDepth" lock "ApplLineType", "ApplDepth" ENDIF

CALL "ui_tabcontrol" parameters controlType = 1, nTabs = 3, gs_ui_current_page = gs_ui_current_page
